body.content:
I trust this message finds you in good health.


I am Dr. Samurai Okai from Ghana. I am a retired government personal
and a political figure.
I am contacting you for joint business collaboration. I am seeking for
investment projects like real estate, communication, energy and more.
Let me know if you have any project that requires funding or expansion
of existing business.  Email me here with your reply at.
(samuraiokai60@gmail.com)

Looking forward to hear from you.


Kind regards,
Dr S. Okai
Email address:  samuraiokai60@gmail.com

header.subject: Compliment of the season and greetings to you.
